      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>This services update is for the Version 3 images.</h2>\n<p>Please see <strong><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/dxp-cloud/latest/en/reference/upgrading-your-dxp-cloud-stack.html\" target=\"_self\">this guide</a></strong> on how to upgrade to the Version 4 release.<br><br>The Version 4 images are backwards compatible, but the environment variables are defaulted to target the new project workspace and the liferay/dxp docker images.<br><br>The following environment variables need to be adjusted to make the version 4 images work in a non-upgraded project.<br><br></p>\n<h3>Backup</h3>\n<div>\n<div><span>LCP_BACKUP_VOLUME_UID=999</span></div>\n<div><span>LCP_BACKUP_VOLUME_GID=999</span></div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n</div>\n<h3>CI</h3>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span>LCP_CI_SCM_JENKINSFILE_HOOKS_DIR=</span><span>\"lcp/ci/\"</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span>LCP_CI_SCM_JENKINSFILE_PATH=</span><span>\"Jenkinsfile\"</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span>LCP_CI_USE_DEFAULT_JENKINSFILE=</span><span>\"false\"</span>\n</div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n</div>\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The services update to 2020.23.1 includes updates to the Liferay service.<br><span></span></p>\n<h2>DXP Stack 2020.23.1</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 727px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 148px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 157px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 498px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Backup</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.12</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.2.12</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/backup:3.2.12</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">CI</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.4</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.2.4</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/jenkins:2.222.1-3.2.4</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Database</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 41.2222px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.9</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 41.2222px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.2.9</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/database:3.2.9</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Liferay</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.22</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>3.0.23</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2.10-sp1-fp5-3.0.23</strong></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:</span>7.1.10-ga1-fp17-3.0.23</strong></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:</span>7.0.10-ga1-fp90-3.0.23</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.0.8</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.8</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">feraycloud/elasticsearch:6.8.6-3.0.8</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">li<span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">feraycloud/elasticsearch:2.4.6-3.0.8</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Webserver</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.2.0</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.2.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">l<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">iferaycloud/nginx:<span>1.16.1-3.2.0</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> Update Instructions</p>\n<p>To apply these updates, update the gradle.properties file the project root folder with the new docker image tags. Here is an example of applying update 2020.23.1 for a 7.2 Liferay project:</p>\n<pre>liferay.workspace.lcp.backup.image=liferaycloud/backup:3.2.12<br>liferay.workspace.lcp.database.image=liferaycloud/database:3.2.9<br>liferay.workspace.lcp.search.image=<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span>feraycloud/elasticsearch:6.8.6-3.0.8</span></span></span></span><br>liferay.workspace.lcp.liferay.image=<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2.10-sp1-fp5-3.0.23</span><br>liferay.workspace.lcp.webserver.image=liferaycloud/nginx:1.16.1-3.2.0<br>liferay.workspace.lcp.jenkins.image=<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">liferaycloud/jenkins:2.222.1-3.2.4</span></pre>\n<p>Once the gradle.properties file contains the updates, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n<pre>git add gradle.properties &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"update dxp cloud stack to 2020.23.1\"</pre>\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>\n<h2>Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 871px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 111px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket Number</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 652px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Liferay</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.23</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">LCPE-1326</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 652px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">apply latest fix packs to liferay</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>"
      },
